T02D1993:189a-0: @189a / las kyi gshin rje'i mchod pa'i cho ga bzhugs so /
T02D1993:189a-2: # // bcom ldan 'das zhe sdang gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1993:189a-3: rang gzhan bar chad zhi ba dang //
T02D1993:189a-4: dngos grub mthar phyin bya ba'i phyir //
T02D1993:189b-0: las kyi gshin rje @189b 'khor bcas kyi //
T02D1993:189b-1: mchod pa'i cho ga 'di ltar bya //
T02D1993:189b-2: rnal 'byor ldan pas mdun bskyed mchod //
T02D1993:189b-3: ri rab bang rim bzhi pa yi //
T02D1993:189b-4: rtse la chos kyi rgyal po ni //
T02D1993:189b-5: nag po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
T02D1993:189b-6: padma nyin byed ma he'i steng //
T02D1993:189b-7: g-yas bskum g-yon brkyang rol pas bzhugs //
T02D1993:189b-8: rdo rje thod dbyug sbrul zhags 'dzin //
T02D1993:189b-9: dar dang stag lpags na bza' gsol //
T02D1993:189b-10: sbrul dang rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan //
T02D1993:189b-11: zhal gdangs mche gtsigs khro gnyer bsdus //
T02D1993:189b-12: spyan gsum drag po'i me stag 'phro //
T02D1993:189b-13: skra ser sma ra gyen du 'dzings //
T02D1993:189b-14: rngam gtsigs gtum po mi sdug pa //
T02D1993:189b-15: mchan khung g-yon na tsa munda //
T02D1993:189b-16: rnam dag rtse gsum 'dzin pa bskyed //
T02D1993:189b-17: de yi phyi rim steg bu la //
T02D1993:189b-18: ya ma r'a dza skyod byed 'bar //
T02D1993:189b-19: ma ru tse dang ral dgu ldan //
T02D1993:189b-20: ded dpon mngags pa pho nya'i tshul //
T02D1993:189b-22: thams cad rdo rjes mtshan pa 'dzin //
T02D1993:189b-23: g-yas su ya ma dhu ti dang //
T02D1993:189b-24: k'a la pa sha dandi nag / ya ma dam shtri lcags kyu dang //
T02D1993:189b-25: zhags pa be con mche ba rnams //
T02D1993:189b-26: 'khor los mtshan pa phyag na bsnams //
T02D1993:189b-27: g-yon du k'a la ra tri dang //
T02D1993:189b-28: gsod ma nag mo chen mo dang //
T02D1993:189b-29: nam gru sha ka li la sogs //
T02D1993:189b-30: me long nad rkyal dru bu dang //
T02D1993:189b-32: g-yon na sho rde dkar nag go //
T02D1993:189b-33: sdo dkar dmar ba'i kha dog can //
T02D1993:189b-34: cha lugs gtso bo bzhin du bskyed //
T02D1993:189b-35: de yi phyi rol stegs bu la //
T02D1993:189b-36: phyogs bzhir rgyal po chen po bzhi //
T02D1993:189b-37: g-yas g-yon gza' brkyang klu chen brgyad //
T02D1993:189b-38: de yi phyi rim stegs bu la//
T02D1993:189b-39: phyogs skyong bcu dang sde brgyad dang //
T02D1993:189b-40: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad rnams //
T02D1993:189b-41: rang rang gzugs sam gtso bo bzhin //
T02D1993:189b-42: 'byung po kun gyis bskor ba bskyed //
T02D1993:189b-43: gnas gsum byin brlabs dbyings nas dgug / dbang bskur rdo rje sems dpa'i rgya //
T02D1993:189b-44: tshogs dang gtor ma'i mchod pa dang //
T02D1993:189b-45: gur phod dang ngar glud dang //
T02D1993:189b-46: nam mkha' ba dan mda' dang 'phang //
T02D1993:189b-47: srog chags sna tshogs ngur ba dang //
T02D1993:189b-48: rin chen lnga dang 'bras bu dang //
T02D1993:189b-49: gling dang gling phran la sogs pas //
T02D1993:189b-50: mchod dang bstod pa las bcol bya //
T02D1993:190a-2: gangs ri'i khrod na rgyal po'i bu //
T02D1993:190a-3: sbyin bdag chen po'i bzhed pa bzhin //
T02D1993:190a-4: bod kyi lugs dang mthun pa 'di //
T02D1993:190a-5: 'gro la phan pa'i ched du bsgrubs //
T02D1993:190a-6: bla ma'i lung dang mi 'gal zhing //
T02D1993:190a-7: gdul bya'i blo dang mthun pa yi //
T02D1993:190a-8: man ngag lha yi rjes gnang nas //
T02D1993:190a-9: bhang+ga la las brjod pa yin //
T02D1993:190a-10: rgya gar shar phyogs kyi pandi ta darpan a'a tsaryas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
